# <type>(<scope>): <summary in imperative, max ~50 chars>
#
# Types: feat | fix | chore | docs | refactor | test | style
# Example:  feat(methodology): collaboration chapter
#
# Body (optional): explain the WHY of the change, not the what (~72 chars).
#
#
# --- Co-authorship ----------------------------------------------------------
# If THIS change was made by two people (pairing, shared code, or a
# suggestion accepted in review), add them below —with a blank line above—.
# Only if it was real joint work; not just for being on the same team.
# The noreply email is on GitHub → Settings → Emails.
#
# Co-authored-by: First Last <ID+user@users.noreply.github.com>
